Drupal 7


### Liste de liens utiles 
[token](http://drupal.org/project/token)

> Tokens are small bits of text that can be placed into larger documents via simple placeholders, like %site-name or [user]. The Token module provides a central API for modules to use these tokens, and expose their own token values.

[token_custom](http://drupal.org/project/token_custom)
 > It gives the user the ability to create custom tokens for specific replacements that can improve other modules relying on the Drupal 7 token API or, for Drupal 6, the Token module.
